The '''Spectacle brooch''' was an ancient [[fibula]] used by the [[Illyrians]]. The spectacle brooch originates in [[Illyria]] and consists of two concentrically wound spirals attached to a pin.<ref>{{cite book|last=Wilkes|first=John J.|title=The Illyrians|location=Oxford|publisher=Blackwell Publishing|year=1995|page=231|isbn=0-631-19807-5|ref=harv}}</ref>

